{"title_page": "Thomas Ortega", "text_new": "{{short description|Argentine footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Thomas Ortega\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| caption = \n| fullname = Thom\u00e1s Sebasti\u00e1n Ortega\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|2000|12|6|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Rafael Calzada, Buenos Aires|Rafael Calzada]], Argentina\n| height = 1.78m\n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| currentclub = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]]\n| clubnumber = 33\n| youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]]\n| years1 = 2020\u2013     | clubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]] | caps1 = 1 | goals1 = 0\n| club-update = 27 March 2020\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Thomas Sebasti\u00e1n Ortega''' (born 6 December 2000) is an Argentine professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]].\n\n==Professional career==\nOn 8 January 2020, Ortega signed his first professional contract with [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lavozdeldiablo.com/independiente/34557-ortega-2022.html|title=Ortega 2022|first=Walter|last=Arci|date=January 8, 2020}}</ref> Ortega made his professional debut with Independiente in a 1-0 [[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] win over [[Racing Club de Avellaneda|Racing Club]] on 9 February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ca.soccerway.com/matches/2020/02/09/argentina/primera-division/racing-club-de-avellaneda/ca-independiente/3070538/|title=Racing Club vs. Independiente - 9 February 2020 - Soccerway|website=ca.soccerway.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|thomas-sebastian-ortega/651094}}\n* [http://clubaindependiente.com/futbol/plantel/perfil/thomasortega Indepentiente Profile]\n\n{{Independiente squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ortega, Thomas}}\n[[Category:2000 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Almirante Brown Partido]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n players]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Argentine footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Thomas Ortega\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| caption = \n| fullname = Thom\u00e1s Sebasti\u00e1n Ortega\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|2000|12|6|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Rafael Calzada, Buenos Aires|Rafael Calzada]], Argentina\n| height = 1.78m\n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| currentclub = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]]\n| clubnumber = 33\n| youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]]\n| years1 = 2020\u2013     | clubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]] | caps1 = 1 | goals1 = 0\n| club-update = 27 March 2020\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Thomas Sebasti\u00e1n Ortega''' (born 6 December 2000) is an Argentine professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]].\n\n==Professional career==\nOn 8 January 2020, Ortega signed his first professional contract with [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente|Independiente]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lavozdeldiablo.com/independiente/34557-ortega-2022.html|title=Ortega 2022|first=Walter|last=Arci|date=January 8, 2020}}</ref> Ortega made his professional debut with Independiente in a 1-0 [[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] win over [[Racing Club de Avellaneda|Racing Club]] on 9 February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ca.soccerway.com/matches/2020/02/09/argentina/primera-division/racing-club-de-avellaneda/ca-independiente/3070538/|title=Racing Club vs. Independiente - 9 February 2020 - Soccerway|website=ca.soccerway.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|thomas-sebastian-ortega/651094/}}\n* [http://clubaindependiente.com/futbol/plantel/perfil/thomasortega Indepentiente Profile]\n\n{{Independiente squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ortega, Thomas}}\n[[Category:2000 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Almirante Brown Partido]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Club Atl\u00e9tico Independiente footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n players]]\n", "name_user": "Zyxw", "label": "safe", "comment": "update external links/templates, misc formatting", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Ortega"}
