ry:Expatriate footballers in Uzbekistan]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Uzbekistan]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Ukraine]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Ukraine]]\n\n\n{{Brazil-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{BLP sources|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Lucas de Oliveira Cunha\n| image = \n| fullname = \n| height = 1.78 m\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1997|7|30}}\n| birth_place = [[Cataguases]], [[Minas Gerais]], Brazil\n| currentclub = [[FC Balkany Zorya|Balkany Zorya]]\n| clubnumber = 77\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| youthyears1 = 2012\u20132014\n| youthclubs1 =[[Friburguense Atl\u00e9tico Clube|Friburguense]]\n| years1 = 2015\u20132016\n| clubs1 = [[Friburguense Atl\u00e9tico Clube|Friburguense]]\n| caps1 = 7\n| goals1 = 1\n| years2 = 2017\n| clubs2 = [[Mogi Mirim Esporte Clube|Mogi Mirim]]\n| caps2 = 2\n| goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2018\n| clubs3 =[[Sociedade Esportiva Matonense|Matonense]]\n| caps3 = 6\n| goals3 = 0\n| years4 = 2019\n| clubs4 = [[Esporte Clube Primavera|Primavera]]\n| caps4 = 8\n| goals4 = 1\n| years5 = 2019\n| clubs5 = [[Surkhon Termez]]\n| caps5 = 7\n| goals5 = 0\n| years6 = 2020\u2013\n| clubs6 =[[FC Balkany Zorya|Balkany Zorya]]\n| caps6 = 0\n| goals6 = 0\n| pcupdate = 21 February 2020\n}}\n\n'''Lucas de Oliveira Cunha''' (born 30 July 1997) is a Brazilian [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for Ukrainian club [[FC Balkany Zorya|Balkany Zorya]].\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|lucas-de-oliveira-cunha/395570/}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Oliveira De Cunha, Lucas}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Minas Gerais]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Friburguense Atl\u00e9tico Clube players]]\n[[Category:Mogi Mirim Esporte Clube players]]\n[[Category:Sociedade Esportiva Matonense pla