{"title_page": "Prince Nxumalo", "text_new": "{{short description|South African footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2013}}\n{{Use South African English|date=November 2013}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Prince Nxumalo\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| fullname = Mfanafuthi Prince Nxumalo\n| height = 1.83 m\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1990|5|18}}\n| birth_place = [[Durban]], South Africa\n| currentclub = [[Baroka F.C.|Baroka]]\n| clubnumber = 35\n| position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| youthyears1 =\n| youthclubs1 = Khanya FC\n| youthyears2 =\n| youthclubs2 = Benfica\n| youthyears3 =\n| youthclubs3 = Amaqhawe Football Academy\n| years1 = 2010\u20132012\n| clubs1 = [[F.C. Cape Town|Cape Town]]\n| caps1 = \n| goals1 = \n| years2 = 2012\u20132015\n| clubs2 = [[SuperSport United F.C.|SuperSport United]]\n| caps2 = 17\n| goals2 = 1\n| years3 = 2014\n| clubs3 = \u2192 [[F.C. Cape Town|Cape Town]] (loan)\n| caps3 = 14\n| goals3 = 7\n| years4 = 2015\n| clubs4 = \u2192 [[Lamontville Golden Arrows F.C.|Golden Arrows]] (loan)\n| caps4 = 14\n| goals4 = 4\n| years5 = 2015\u20132019\n| clubs5 = [[Ajax Cape Town F.C.|Ajax Cape Town]]\n| caps5 = 76\n| goals5 = 24\n| years6 = 2019\n| clubs6 = [[Bidvest Wits F.C.|Bidvest Wits]]\n| caps6 = 0\n| goals6 = 0\n| years7 = 2019\u2013\n| clubs7 = [[Baroka F.C.|Baroka]]\n| caps7 = 9\n| goals7 = 1\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 = \n| nationalcaps1 = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| pcupdate = 17:07, 23 March 2020 (UTC)\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Mfanafuthi Prince Nxumalo''' (born 18 May 1990) is a [[South Africa]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Baroka F.C.|Baroka]] as a [[Forward (association football)|Forward]].\n\n==Club career==\nNxumalo joined [[SuperSport United F.C.|SuperSport United]] from [[FC Cape Town]] in August 2012. He made his league debut against [[Ajax Cape Town F.C.|Ajax Cape Town]] on 19 December 2012, scoring a goal.<ref>{{cite web|title=SuperSport claim late winner|url=http://www.sport24.co.za/Soccer/PSL/SuperSport-claim-late-winner-20121219|accessdate=21 November 2013}}</ref> Prince Nxumalo has since moved to Lamontville Goldern Arrows on loan in January 2015.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|mfanafuthi-prince-nxumalo/251315}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Nxumalo, Prince}}\n[[Category:1990 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:South African soccer players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Durban]]\n[[Category:South African Premier Division players]]\n[[Category:National First Division players]]\n[[Category:SuperSport United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:F.C. Cape Town players]]\n[[Category:Lamontville Golden Arrows F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Ajax Cape Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Bidvest Wits F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Baroka F.C. players]]\n\n\n{{SouthAfrica-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|South African footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2013}}\n{{Use South African English|date=November 2013}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Prince Nxumalo\n| image = \n| image_size = \n| fullname = Mfanafuthi Prince Nxumalo\n| height = {{height|m=1.83}}\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1990|5|18}}\n| birth_place = [[Durban]], South Africa\n| currentclub = [[Baroka F.C.|Baroka]]\n| clubnumber = 35\n| position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| youthyears1 =\n| youthclubs1 = Khanya FC\n| youthyears2 =\n| youthclubs2 = Benfica\n| youthyears3 =\n| youthclubs3 = Amaqhawe Football Academy\n| years1 = 2010\u20132012\n| clubs1 = [[F.C. Cape Town|Cape Town]]\n| caps1 = \n| goals1 = \n| years2 = 2012\u20132015\n| clubs2 = [[SuperSport United F.C.|SuperSport United]]\n| caps2 = 17\n| goals2 = 1\n| years3 = 2014\n| clubs3 = \u2192 [[F.C. Cape Town|Cape Town]] (loan)\n| caps3 = 14\n| goals3 = 7\n| years4 = 2015\n| clubs4 = \u2192 [[Lamontville Golden Arrows F.C.|Golden Arrows]] (loan)\n| caps4 = 14\n| goals4 