 football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Runcorn Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Fleetwood Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Nantwich Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:Northern Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Salford City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Chorley F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Curzon Ashton F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Trafford F.C. players]]\n[[Category:A.F.C. Fylde players]]\n[[Category:National League (English football) players]]\n", "name_user": "Zyxw", "label": "safe", "comment": "update external links/templates, misc formatting", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nick_Haughton"}
