egory:Club Atl\u00e9tico Patronato footballers]]\n[[Category:Club Atl\u00e9tico Paran\u00e1 players]]\n\n\n{{Argentina-footy-defender-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Brian Negro\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Brian Negro\n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|1997|9|8|df=y}}\n| birth_place    = [[Bovril, Argentina]]\n| height         = \n| position       = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| currentclub    = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Patronato|Patronato]]\n| clubnumber     = 20\n| years1         = 2018\u2013     | clubs1 = [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Patronato|Patronato]]            | caps1 = 1  | goals1 = 0\n| years2         = 2018\u20132019 | clubs2 = \u2192[[Club Atl\u00e9tico Paran\u00e1|Atl\u00e9tico Paran\u00e1]] (loan) | caps2 = 19 | goals2 = 1\n| club-update    = 10 April 2020\n| nationalteam-update = \n| medaltemplates =\n}}\n'''Brian Negro''' (born 8 September 1997) is an Argentine professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Patronato|Patronato]].\n\n==Club career==\nNegro made his professional debut with Patronato in a 1-0 [[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n]] loss to [[Club Atl\u00e9tico V\u00e9lez Sarsfield|V\u00e9lez Sarsfield]] on 9 December 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ca.soccerway.com/matches/2019/12/09/argentina/primera-division/club-atletico-patronato/club-atletico-velez-sarsfield/3070509/|title=Patronato vs. V\u00e9lez Sarsfield - 9 December 2019 - Soccerway|website=ca.soccerway.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n \n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|brian-negro/501808/}}\n\n{{Club Atl\u00e9tico Patronato squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Negro, Brian}}\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Entre R\u00edos Province]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Association footba